{"word":"Lion","slug":"lion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Lion</b> King of beasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=8'>Mic 5:8</a><br/> Fierceness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=4&verse=10'>Job 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=28&verse=8'>Job 28:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=7&verse=2'>Psa 7:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=13'>Pro 22:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=15'>Jer 2:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=19'>Jer 49:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=44'>Jer 50:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=8'>Hos 13:8</a><br/> The roaring of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=22&verse=13'>Psa 22:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=2'>Pro 20:2</a><br/> Strength of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=30'>Pro 30:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=13'>Isa 38:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1&verse=6'>Joe 1:6</a><br/> Instincts of, in taking prey<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=10&verse=9'>Psa 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=12'>Psa 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=3&verse=10'>Lam 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=4'>Amo 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=2&verse=12'>Nah 2:12</a><br/> Lair of, in the jungles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=7'>Jer 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapte